Sentencas: A novel route was developed for preparing Ag-CGO porous cermets as the anode materials for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells (ITSOFCs) using Ce0.8Gd0.2O1.9(CGO) electrolyte.
Titulo: Porous Ag-CGO cermets as anode materials for ITSOFC using CO fuel

Sentencas: Porous CGO was prepared by leaching MgO from MgO-CGO ceramics with acetic acid and then impregnated with AgNO3 solution.
Titulo: Porous Ag-CGO cermets as anode materials for ITSOFC using CO fuel

Sentencas: Porous cermet that contained 45 wt% Ag with the optimal porosity of 48% was a promising anode material for ITSOFCs using CO as the fuel.
Titulo: Porous Ag-CGO cermets as anode materials for ITSOFC using CO fuel
